               <li class="pages_text">6.5. To enforce any of the foregoing rights or if you have any other questions about our Website or this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contacts" class="pages_link">contact us</a>.</li>

               <p class="pages_text terms_conditions_span">7. Links to other sites</p>
