               <p class="pages_text terms_conditions_span">9. Automated decision-making and profiling</p>
               <li class="pages_text">9.1. In the event that we use personal data for the purposes of automated decision-making and those decisions have a legal (or similarly significant effect) on you, you have the right to challenge to such decisions under GDPR, requesting human intervention, expressing their own point of view, and obtaining an explanation of the decision from us.</li>
               <li class="pages_text">9.2. The right described in section 11.1 does not apply in the following circumstances:</li>
